Data. We consider 50 subjects, 25 encyclopedic entities such as elon musk, and 25 commonsense concepts, such as jogging (Full list in Appendix (ref)). Our intuition behind these choices is diversity: (i) in types, e.g., activities, occupations, people; and (ii) in popularity, e.g., tom cruise (a famous hollywood actor) and peri gilpin (a less known tv actor).